note: Sample fulfillment vectors for key commodities. Expand with all 133 commodities.

durabilitySchema.description: Schema for durability fields on commodities

fields.durability: consumable | durable | permanent - how the commodity is used
fields.durationCycles: number - how many cycles before expiry (null for consumable/permanent)
fields.effectDecayRate: number - effectiveness loss per cycle (0 = no decay)
fields.category: string - slot category for ownership limits
fields.maxOwned: number - max instances character can own (default 1)
